<h2 class="bold font-l">Ratatouille: Remy in control</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Remy and Linguini use a tactic in which Remy will control Linguini by pulling on his hair like a marionette puppet. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/PeoplePuppets" class='trope-example-link'>People Puppets</a></p>
